{"title":"Find your Flow State w/ B.Harms x Blacksmith Cycle “Special Projects” Kit","link":"https://bikerumor.com/b-harms-x-blacksmith-cycle-special-projects-kit/","date":1714653610000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-3-1536x1011.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1011\" alt=\"B Harms Special Projects Cycling Jerseys by Blacksmith Cycles\" /></p>\n<p>Looking for something subdued but unique? The limited edition artist series from Blacksmith Cycle features custom art by B.Harms + Special Projects for an exclusive spring collection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The project is a collaboration between Mike Yakubowicz, owner of Toronto’s specialty bicycle retailer Blacksmith Cycle, artist Brad Harms, and Todd McCallum, a former racer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1026\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-1536x1026.jpg\" alt=\"B Harms Special Projects Cycling bibshorts on a man and a woman\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-2.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The art is from the B.Harms + Special Projects “Flow State” series, based on Brad’s vibrant and expressive paintings. They say that “Much like the perfect ride, they highlight the balance of flow and control, method and imagination.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1468\" height=\"1197\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1.jpg\" alt=\"B Harms Special Projects Cycling kits by Blacksmith Cycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1.jpg 1468w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1-297x242.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1-120x98.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BLACKSMITH-CYCLE-x-B-Harms-special-projects-kit-1-768x626.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The kit is produced by Givelo and the complete collection Includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>G90/GVL custom jersey</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lacefly Pro bib shorts (in two colors)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gravel Tech-T</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gilet with 2-way zipper technology</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Super Light Base Layer</li>\n\n\n\n<li>G-socks</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Essentials Cap</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Bibs will be available in both men’s and women’s sizing while other items are all unisex. All pieces are designed by B.Harms+Special Projects in collaboration with Blacksmith Cycle. Pre-orders close end-of-day Saturday, May 4, 2024, with delivery near the end of May/early June. Order at link below.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1149\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings.jpg\" alt=\"artist bradley harms standing behind two giant paintings.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings.jpg 1400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings-297x244.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings-120x98.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Bradley-harms-holding-colour-paintings-768x630.jpg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Bradley Harms and his art.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Blacksmith Cycle will also be selling prints of the original “Flow State” work of art, which is included free with any order of the complete cycling kit collection. Matching Elite custom water bottles and Givelo Musettes are also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://blacksmithcycle.com/en-us/collections/blacksmith-cycle-ss24\" target=\"_blank\">BlacksmithCycle.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/b-harms-x-blacksmith-cycle-special-projects-kit/\">Find your Flow State w/ B.Harms x Blacksmith Cycle “Special Projects” Kit</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"cec5dc12268c499d936a25bf55dea4fab6a1a07bb0efb04238456e0c616b5acf","category":"Cycling"}